<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ofsted> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Ofsted is the Office for Standards in Education, Children’s Services and Skills. We inspect services providing education and skills for learners of all ages. We also inspect and regulate services that care for children and young people. Ofsted is a non-ministerial department."@en .
